Ground color of body yellowish brown with dark brown maculation (
Fig. 38
). Small sized with body length 14.0 mm, head width maximum 4.0 mm; length of hind femur 4.5 mm .

Thorax—Thorax almost as broad as the transverse diameter of head; pronotum strongly developed (
Fig. 24
) with 3 transverse depressions; synthorax fringed with long setae; wing pads strongly divergent extending to basal 1 / 3 of S 7 . Legs long and slender, femora and tibiae each with more than 10 long, erect, pointed setae dorsally and ventrally; femora yellowish with two dark brown stripes submedially; tibiae yellowish with dark brown maculation basely.
